   Nigeria: 'Africa's Biggest Jesus Statue' Unveiled in Nigeria\n          </h1>\n         </div>\n         <!--/.content-->\n        </div>\n        <!--/.heading-->\n        <div class=\"sharebar solid\">\n         <div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_default_style\">\n          <a class=\"button_twitter\" data-account=\"allafrica\" data-full-url=\"http://allafrica.com/stories/201601020082.html\" data-height=\"450\" data-short-url=\"http://allafrica.com/stories/201601020082.html\" data-title=\"'Africa's Biggest Jesus Statue' Unveiled in Nigeria\" data-width=\"575\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fallafrica.com%2Fstories%2F201601020082.html&amp;text=%27Africa%27s%20Biggest%20Jesus%20Statue%27%20Unveiled%20in%20Nigeria&amp;via=allafrica&amp;related=allafrica,allafricafrench,allafricasport\">\n           <div class=\"share-button twitter\">\n            <span class=\"icon\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"action\">\n             tweet\n            </span>\n           </div>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"button_facebook\" data-full-url=\"http://allafrica.com/stories/201601020082.html\" data-height=\"450\" data-width=\"575\">\n           <div class=\"share-button facebook\">\n            <span class=\"icon\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"action\">\n             share\n            </span>\n           </div>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"button_google_plus\" data-full-url=\"http://allafrica.com/stories/201601020082.html\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"600\">\n           <div class=\"share-button google_plus\">\n            <span class=\"icon\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"action\">\n             Google+\n            </span>\n           </div>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"button_comment\" href=\"#comments\">\n           <div class=\"share-button comment\">\n            <span class=\"icon\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"action\">\n            